subject: Greetings,
body:
Greetings,
I am Cameron, a financial analyst. I do have some business discussion I would like us to deliberate on that would yield good profit. I can assure you that you would like it.
Get back to me for more information.
Thanks
Cameron Gundersun

subject: Re:   Greetings,
body:
Hello Cameron,

Thank you for reaching out. I'm always interested in hearing about new business opportunities. Could you please provide more details about this venture? What kind of business is it and how does it work?

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Juan
